'''灰原雞'''（''Gallus sonneratii''）是一種分布于[[印度|印度]]的[[原鸡属|原鸡属]]物种，是[[原鸡|原鸡]]、[[黑尾原鸡|黑尾原鸡]]等的近親。

== 特徵 ==
[[File:Sonnerathuhn.jpg|thumb]]
[[File:Coq_de_Sonnerat_MHNT.jpg|thumb]]
雄性灰原雞的冠黑色，有赭色斑點，身體呈灰色。頸上[[羽毛|羽毛]]較長，呈深色，末端呈黃色及片狀，可以造成高質的假蠅。牠們的腳紅色，肉垂並不像[[原雞|原雞]]般大。雄雞的腳有距，雌雞一般都沒有。<ref>{{Cite journal en|author=Editors|year=1954|title=Occurrence of spurs in the female Junglefowl (''Gallus sonnerati'')|journal=J. Bombay Nat. Hist. Soc.|volume=52|issue=2-3|pages=603-604}}</ref>中央尾羽較長及呈鐮刀狀。雄雞在[[夏天|夏天]]或[[繁殖|繁殖]]季節後會脫下鮮艷的頸羽。<ref>{{Cite journal en|author=Morejohn, G. V.|year=1968|title=Study of the plumage of the four species of the genus ''Gallus gallus''|url=https://archive.org/details/sim_condor_1968-01_70_1/page/56|journal=The Condor|volume=70|pages=56-65}}</ref>雌雞較沉色，下身有黑白斑紋，腳黃色。牠們棲息在底層的叢林。牠們會於晨暮間啼叫。牠們以小群居住，於2月至5月繁殖。<ref name=rasmussen>{{Cite book en|author=Rasmussen PC & JC Anderton|year=2005|title=Birds of South Asia: The Ripley Guide. Vol. 2|publisher=Smithsonian Institution and Lynx Edicions|pages=132}}</ref>牠們每次生4-7隻蛋，蛋呈淡奶白色，約21天就能孵化。雖然很多時在地上生活，牠們也可以飛上樹上棲息或逃避[[掠食者|掠食者]]。

{{audio|G-sonnerati.ogg|雄雞的啼聲}}{{audio|Greyjunglefowl.ogg|其他叫聲}}{{audio|Greyjunglefowl1.ogg|叫聲}}

灰原雞主要吃[[竹|竹]]的[[種子|種子]]、[[漿果|漿果]]、[[昆蟲|昆蟲]]及[[白蟻|白蟻]]。

灰原雞的[[種小名|種小名]]是為紀念[[法國|法國]]探險家[[皮埃爾·索納拉特|皮埃爾·索納拉特]]（Pierre Sonnerat）。

== 分佈及演化 ==
灰原雞主要分佈在[[印度|印度]]半島，伸延至[[古吉拉特邦|古吉拉特邦]]、[[中央邦|中央邦]]及[[拉賈斯坦邦|拉賈斯坦邦]]南部。牠們與[[原雞|原雞]]稍為重疊了北方的分佈地。<ref name=rasmussen/>牠們可能與原雞混種了家養的[[雞|雞]]。<ref name= Eriksson>{{Cite journal en|author=Eriksson J, Larson G, Gunnarsson U, Bed'hom B, Tixier-Boichard M, et al.|year=2008|title=Identification of the Yellow Skin Gene Reveals a Hybrid Origin of the Domestic Chicken|journal=PLoS Genet|url=http://www.plosgenetics.org/article/info:doi/10.1371/journal.pgen.1000010|access-date=2009-05-02|archive-date=2012-05-25|archive-url=https://archive.today/20120525080505/http://www.plosgenetics.org/article/info:doi/10.1371/journal.pgen.1000010|dead-url=yes}}</ref>灰原雞可能因行為差異與[[基因|基因]]不相容等原因而被孤立起來。<ref>{{Cite journal en|author=Morejohn, G. Victor|year=1968|title=Breakdown of Isolation Mechanisms in Two Species of Captive Junglefowl (''Gallus gallus'' and ''Gallus sonneratii'')|url=https://archive.org/details/sim_evolution_1968-09_22_3/page/576|journal=Evolution|volume=22|issue=3|pages=576-582}}</ref>一些研究發現牠們與[[黑尾原雞|黑尾原雞]]較原雞更為接近<ref>{{Cite journal en|author=Akishinonomiya Fumihito, Tetsuo Miyake, Masaru Takada, Ryosuke Shingut, Toshinori Endo, Takashi Gojobori, Norio Kondo, And Susumu Ohno|year=1996|title=Monophyletic origin and unique dispersal patterns of domestic fowls|journal=Proc. Natl. Acad. Sci.|volume=93|pages=6792-6795|url=http://www.pnas.org/cgi/reprint/93/13/6792.pdf|access-date=2009-05-02|archive-date=2007-10-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20071001061504/http://www.pnas.org/cgi/reprint/93/13/6792.pdf|dead-url=no}}</ref>，但另有一些研究卻因混種的緣故發不明朗的分類。<ref>{{Cite journal en|author=Nishibori, M. ; Shimogiri, T. ; Hayashi, T. ; Yasue, H.|year=2005|title=Molecular evidence for hybridization of species in the genus ''Gallus'' except for ''Gallus varius''|journal=Animal Genetics|volume=36|issue=5|pages=367-375}}</ref>在家養雞中的一種內在反轉錄病毒的基因序列，也在灰原雞的[[基因組|基因組]]中出現，顯示這種[[病毒|病毒]]的[[DNA|DNA]]很早就與[[原雞屬|原雞屬]]的基因組混合。<ref>{{Cite journal en|author=Sacci, MA; K Howes & K Venugopal|year=2001|title=Intact EAV-HP endogenous retrovirus in Sonnerat's Jungle Fowl|journal=Journal of Virology|volume=75|issue=4|pages=2029-2032|url=http://jvi.asm.org/cgi/reprint/75/4/2029.pdf}}</ref>

== 保育狀況 ==
灰原雞每平方公里就有19.8群，一群平均約有1.3隻。雄雞與雌雞的比例為1:1.2，最喜歡棲息在低至中度冠層的[[森林|森林]]。<ref>{{Cite journal en|author=Sathyakumar, S|year=2006|url=http://www.bnhs.org/bo/documents/JBNHS_103_1/Sathyakumar.pdf|title=Habitat use by Grey Junglefowl ''Gallus sonneratii'' Temminck at Mundanthurai Plateau, Tamil Nadu.|journal=Journ. Bombay Nat. Hist. Soc.|volume=103|issue=1|pages=57-61|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20100706044828/http://www.bnhs.org/bo/documents/JBNHS_103_1/Sathyakumar.pdf|archivedate=2010-07-06}}</ref>

灰原雞受到捕獵及失去棲息地的威脅。用牠們的[[羽毛|羽毛]]來製作假蠅也令牠們的數量減少。<ref>{{Cite journal en|author=Wayre, P|year=1976|title=Sonnerat's - a junglefowl threatened by fishermen|journal=Newsl. for Birdwatchers|volume=16|issue=5|pages=1-3}}</ref>

